                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"headline-information\"\u003eHeadline Information\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDepartment\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eGovernment Legal Department\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDivision\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eEmployment Group\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eJob title\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDirector\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eLocation\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eLondon or Leeds\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eSalary\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cabbr title=\"Senior Civil Service\"\u003eSCS\u003c/abbr\u003e Payband 2 - £90,500\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eApplication deadline\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e9am on Monday 29 July 2019\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"vacancy-details\"\u003eVacancy details\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-legal-department\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eGovernment Legal Department (\u003cabbr title=\"Government Legal Department\"\u003eGLD\u003c/abbr\u003e)\u003c/a\u003e is seeking a Director of its Employment Group.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou will be directly responsible for the employment law advisory and litigation service provided by \u003cabbr title=\"Government Legal Department\"\u003eGLD\u003c/abbr\u003e and for the operational management of one of the single largest concentration of employment lawyers in the \u003cabbr title=\"United Kingdom\"\u003eUK\u003c/abbr\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis includes the daily operation and people management of the Employment Group, client relationship management and consultation on difficult, important, or sensitive case issues.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAs a member of the senior team within \u003cabbr title=\"Government Legal Department\"\u003eGLD\u003c/abbr\u003e, you will help shape and deliver the \u003cabbr title=\"Government Legal Department\"\u003eGLD\u003c/abbr\u003e vision for the whole of the organisation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou will also be part of a network of colleagues who work corporately across Whitehall to establish best practice within the legal profession. For example by considering how the \u003cabbr title=\"Government Legal Department\"\u003eGLD\u003c/abbr\u003e can work corporately to reduce legal risk and cost to government, and to drive change within the civil service as a whole.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"apply\"\u003eApply\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor further information on the post and details on how to apply, please visit the \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.civilservicejobs.service.gov.uk/csr/jobs.cgi?jcode=1641250\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eCivil Service Jobs Website.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003csection class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-display-none-print govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\" data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail\"\u003e\n    \u003ca class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link=\u0027{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}\u0027 href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5d288e18e5274a14e426cfba/Candidate_Info_Pack_GLD_Director_Employment_Group.pdf\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--custom\" src=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5d288e17ed915d2febd74acb/thumbnail_Candidate_Info_Pack_GLD_Director_Employment_Group.pdf.png\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"gem-c-attachment__details\"\u003e\n    \u003ch2 class=\"gem-c-attachment__title\"\u003e\n      \u003ca class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" data-ga4-link=\u0027{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}\u0027 href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5d288e18e5274a14e426cfba/Candidate_Info_Pack_GLD_Director_Employment_Group.pdf\"\u003eCandidate Info Pack GLD Director Employment Group\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n      \u003cp class=\"gem-c-attachment__metadata\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\"\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment__abbr\"\u003ePDF\u003c/abbr\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\"\u003e796 KB\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment__attribute\"\u003e19 pages\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n      \u003cp class=\"gem-c-attachment__metadata\"\u003eThis file may not be suitable for users of assistive technology.\u003c/p\u003e\n      \u003cdetails class=\"gem-c-details govuk-details govuk-!-margin-bottom-3\" data-module=\"govuk-details gem-details ga4-event-tracker\"\u003e\n  \u003csummary class=\"govuk-details__summary\" data-details-track-click=\"\" data-ga4-event=\u0027{\"event_name\":\"select_content\",\"type\":\"detail\",\"text\":\"Request an accessible format.\",\"section\":\"Request an accessible format.\",\"index_section\":1}\u0027\u003e\n    \u003cspan class=\"govuk-details__summary-text\" data-ga4-expandable\u003e\n      Request an accessible format.\n    \u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/summary\u003e  \u003cdiv class=\"govuk-details__text\"\u003e\n    \n        If you use assistive technology (such as a screen reader) and need a version of this document in a more accessible format, please email \u003ca href=\"mailto:govtrainees@tmpw.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003egovtrainees@tmpw.co.uk\u003c/a\u003e. Please tell us what format you need. It will help us if you say what assistive technology you use.\